webrtc.callStartTip: Click to start a video call
webrtc.callRunningTip: This call is already in progress. Click to show the call window.
webrtc.refreshTryAgainContactAdmin: Sila muat semula halaman dan cuba lagi. Jika ralat berterusan, sila hubungi pentadbir anda dengan rujukan ralat ini.
webrtc.errorAddCall: The call could not be started due to a server error. Please try again. If the problem persists, please contact your administrator.
webrtc.errorOpeningCall: An error occurred while opening the call window. Please refresh the page and try again. If the error persists, please contact your administrator.
webrtc.callWindowNotOpen: Call window could not be opened. Please check if it was blocked by your browser.
webrtc.errorReadUserStatus: Error reading user status information from the server
webrtc.errorReadCall: Error reading call information from the server
webrtc.errorSubscribeUser: Failed to establish a server-to-browser channel for communicating user updates. Please refresh the page and try again. If the problem persists, please contact your administrator.
webrtc.errorSubscribeCall: Failed to establish a server-to-browser channel for call updates. Please refresh the page and try again. If the problem persists, please contact your administrator.
webrtc.yourBrowserNotSupportWebrtc: Your browser does not support WebRTC calls
webrtc.notInitialized: Penyambung panggilan video WebRTC tidak dimulakan dengan betul. Sila tutup tetingkap ini dan cuba lagi.
webrtc.audioVideoRequired: Mikrofon dan / atau kamera diperlukan untuk membuat panggilan
webrtc.accessDenied: Tidak dapat membuka peranti media disebabkan ralat akses atau kebenaran. Pastikan peranti anda disambungkan dan tidak digunakan oleh aplikasi lain.
